recipes.title: Fiore's "Roast Beef and Mutz" Sandwich Recreation
recipes.description: Recreate the legendary 'Roast Beef and Mutz' sandwich from Fiore's Deli in Hoboken, NJ. This recipe focuses on achieving the signature rare, thinly sliced roast beef, the creamy fresh mozzarella, and the perfect Italian hero roll that makes this classic a Thursday and Saturday favorite.
